title: [Gyldemar Forest, Overgrown Path]
description: The path thins slightly, the foliage somehow pushed back.  Some of the taller grasses have become brittle and few reach higher then two feet.  Uprooted bushes lie here and there, most blackened.

The path thins slightly, the foliage somewhat pushed back into the night.  Some of the taller grasses have become brittle and few reach higher then two feet.  Uprooted bushes lie here and there, most blackened.
